Name: os_restrictemail
Author: Adam
Category: OperServ
Last updated: 2012-06-25T09:33:18+01:00

Adds the command RESTRICTEMAIL to OperServ which prevents users from using specific email addresses.

Contains one configuration option, RestrictEmailAction. Set to 0 (default) to only warn users, and 1 to AKILL new users who try to register with an email on this list.

Version 1.0 supports Anope 1.8.7
